flowchart TD
  %% Authentication and route handling
  subgraph AuthFlow[Authentication]
    V[Visitor] -->|akses /| Root[/]
    Root -->|redirect| Login[Login/Register page]
    Login -->|submit login| Authenticate[AuthenticatedSessionController:store]
    Authenticate -->|success| VerifyEmail{Email verified?}
    VerifyEmail -->|yes| Dashboard[DashboardController:index]
    VerifyEmail -->|no| EmailPrompt[VerifyEmail prompt]
    Login -->|register| Register[RegisteredUserController:store]
    Register -->|success| VerifyEmail
    Dashboard -->|role=ormawa| D1[Ormawa Dashboard]
    Dashboard -->|role=bauak| D2[BAUAK Dashboard]
    Dashboard -->|role=warek3| D3[Warek3 Dashboard]
    Dashboard -->|role=admin| D4[Admin Dashboard]
  end

  %% Ormawa workflow
  subgraph OrmawaFlow[Ormawa]
    D1 -->|akses profile| ProfileMenu[ProfileController:edit]
    ProfileMenu -->|ubah data| ProfileUpdate[ProfileController:update]
    ProfileMenu -->|akun delete| ProfileDelete[ProfileController:destroy]
    ProfileUpdate -->|validasi| ProfileValid{Profile valid?}
    ProfileValid -->|yes| OrmawaHome[Ormawa main menu]
    ProfileValid -->|no| ProfileMenu

    OrmawaHome -->|buat pengajuan| CreateForm[PengajuanKegiatanController:create]
    CreateForm -->|submit| Store[PengajuanKegiatanController:store]
    Store -->|validasi input| Validation{Form valid?}
    Validation -->|no| CreateForm
    Validation -->|yes| SavePengajuan[Create PengajuanKegiatan]
    SavePengajuan -->|upload proposal| SaveProposal[Proposal::create]
    SavePengajuan -->|upload RAB| SaveRAB[Rab::create]
    SavePengajuan -->|buat surat rekomendasi draft| SaveDraftSR[SuratRekomendasi::create(status=draft)]
    SavePengajuan -->|buat notifikasi| NotifyBAUAK[sendNotification ke BAUAK]
    SavePengajuan -->|hasil| StatusDiajukan[status=diajukan]
    StatusDiajukan -->|tampil| OrmawaHome

    OrmawaHome -->|lihat daftar| ListPengajuan[PengajuanKegiatanController:index]
    ListPengajuan -->|filter/search| Filter[search/status/date filters]
    OrmawaHome -->|buka | Show[PengajuanKegiatanController:show]
    Show -->|bisa edit? | CanEdit{status in draft/revisi_bauak/ditolak?}
    CanEdit -->|yes| Edit[PengajuanKegiatanController:edit]
    CanEdit -->|no| Show
    Edit -->|submit update| Update[PengajuanKegiatanController:update]
    Update -->|validasi| UpdateValid{Form valid?}
    UpdateValid -->|no| Edit
    UpdateValid -->|yes| SaveUpdate[PengajuanKegiatan update]
    SaveUpdate -->|replace files| ReplaceFiles[Proposal/Rab update if uploaded]
    SaveUpdate -->|reset status| ResetDiajukan[status=diajukan]
    SaveUpdate -->|notify| NotifyBAUAK2[sendNotification ke BAUAK]
    ResetDiajukan --> OrmawaHome

    OrmawaHome -->|export csv| ExportCSV[PengajuanKegiatanController:exportCSV]
    OrmawaHome -->|print view| PrintView[PengajuanKegiatanController:printView]
    OrmawaHome -->|notifikasi| NotifList[NotifikasiController:index]
    NotifList -->|read satu| MarkRead[NotifikasiController:read]
    NotifList -->|read semua| MarkAllRead[NotifikasiController:read-all]
    NotifList -->|hapus| DeleteNotif[NotifikasiController:destroy]
  end

  %% BAUAK workflow
  subgraph BauakFlow[BAUAK]
    D2 -->|lihat dashboard| BauakHome[Dashboard BAUAK]
    BauakHome -->|lihat daftar| BauakIndex[VerifikasiBauakController:index]
    BauakIndex -->|buka| BauakShow[VerifikasiBauakController:show]
    BauakShow -->|verifikasi| VerifyForm[VerifikasiBauakController:verify]
    VerifyForm -->|submit| VerifyAction[Validate status/catatan]
    VerifyAction -->|disetujui| ApprovedBauak[status=disetujui_bauak]
    VerifyAction -->|revisi| RevisionBauak[status=revisi_bauak]
    VerifyAction -->|ditolak| RejectedBauak[status=ditolak]
    ApprovedBauak -->|proposal/rab final| FinalizeDocs[Proposal/Rab status=final]
    VerifyAction -->|kirim notifikasi Ormawa| NotifyOrmawa[sendNotification ke Ormawa]
    ApprovedBauak -->|kirim notifikasi Warek3| NotifyWarek3[sendNotification ke Warek3]
    BauakHome -->|lihat riwayat| BauakHistory[VerifikasiBauak records]
  end

  %% Warek3 workflow
  subgraph Warek3Flow[Warek3]
    D3 -->|lihat dashboard| Warek3Home[Dashboard Warek3]
    Warek3Home -->|lihat pengajuan| WarekIndex[PersetujuanWarek3Controller:index]
    WarekIndex -->|buka| WarekShow[PersetujuanWarek3Controller:show]
    WarekShow -->|approve| WarekApprove[PersetujuanWarek3Controller:approve]
    WarekShow -->|reject| WarekReject[PersetujuanWarek3Controller:reject]
    WarekApprove -->|create persetujuan| SaveApproval[PersetujuanWarek3::create(status=disetujui)]
    WarekApprove -->|update pengajuan| ApprovedWarek3[status=disetujui_warek3]
    WarekApprove -->|notif Ormawa| NotifyOrmawaFinal[sendNotification ke Ormawa]
    WarekReject -->|create persetujuan| SaveReject[PersetujuanWarek3::create(status=ditolak)]
    WarekReject -->|update pengajuan| RejectedWarek3[status=ditolak]
    WarekReject -->|notif Ormawa| NotifyOrmawaReject[sendNotification ke Ormawa]
    Warek3Home -->|monitoring| Monitoring[PersetujuanWarek3Controller:monitoring]
    Monitoring -->|filter| MonitoringFilter[bulan/ormawa filter]
  end

  %% Admin workflow
  subgraph AdminFlow[Admin]
    D4 -->|lihat dashboard| AdminHome[Dashboard Admin]
    AdminHome -->|kelola ormawa| AdminOrmawa[OrmawaController resource]
    AdminHome -->|kelola pengajuan| AdminPengajuan[PengajuanKegiatanController resource]
    AdminHome -->|lihat laporan| AdminReport[LaporanController]
    AdminOrmawa -->|index/create/edit| OrmawaCRUD[manage Ormawa records]
    AdminPengajuan -->|index/show/edit/delete| PengajuanCRUD[manage Pengajuan records]
  end

  %% Status transitions
  ApprovedBauak --> WarekIndex
  RevisionBauak --> OrmawaHome
  RejectedBauak --> OrmawaHome
  ApprovedWarek3 --> Completed[Pengajuan selesai]
  RejectedWarek3 --> Completed
  NotifyWarek3 -.->|workflow| D3

  %% Cross-role interactions
  NotifyBAUAK -.-> BauakIndex
  NotifyBAUAK2 -.-> BauakIndex
  NotifyOrmawa -.-> NotifList
  NotifyOrmawaFinal -.-> NotifList
  NotifyOrmawaReject -.-> NotifList

  %% Notes
  MarkRead -.-> NotifList
  MarkAllRead -.-> NotifList
  DeleteNotif -.-> NotifList
  ExportCSV -.-> ListPengajuan
  PrintView -.-> ListPengajuan
  OrmawaHome -.->|route /pengajuan| ListPengajuan
